title: This Bollywood Actress’ Holiday Photos Will Give You A Major Bout Of Envy
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 27 . 2017 
Summer’s nearly here, which means it’s time to take off on vacations and spend some time by the beach… and that’s exactly what our Bollywood celebrities are doing. Actress Bruna Abdullah is currently holidaying in Brazil and she looks like she’s having a blast. PS – How does one look so sexy all the damn time? #Jealous. 
Here are photos. A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 21, 2017 at 7:40pm PDT A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 22, 2017 at 10:37am PDT A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 22, 2017 at 10:41am PDT A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 24, 2017 at 8:57am PDT A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 23, 2017 at 8:44am PDT A post shared by Bruna Abdullah (@brunaabdullah) on Mar 23, 2017 at 7:25am PDT 
Definitely jealous!
